The paper discusses the challenges of managing and preserving large datasets and their interdependencies, which are key concerns in the field of database systems (cs.DB). The paper also proposes a solution for preserving evolving structured interlinked data, which involves the use of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques. Additionally, the paper focuses on the Linked Data Paradigm, which is a topic of interest in the field of digital libraries (cs.DL). Finally, the paper discusses the problems that occur in applications and proposes a direction for a solution, which is relevant to the field of software engineering (cs.SE).
